      <p begin="00:24.550" end="00:27.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:24.550" end="00:24.700">Aren</span><span begin="00:24.730" end="00:24.770">'t</span> <span begin="00:24.770" end="00:24.830">you</span> <span begin="00:24.900" end="00:25.420">some</span><span begin="00:25.530" end="00:25.710">thing</span> <span begin="00:26.080" end="00:26.310">to</span> <span begin="00:26.310" end="00:26.410">ad</span><span begin="00:26.510" end="00:27.040">mi</span><span begin="00:27.110" end="00:27.450">re?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你难道不值得令人赞叹吗？</span></p>
