      <p begin="00:30.390" end="00:32.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:30.390" end="00:30.490">And</span> <span begin="00:30.490" end="00:30.540">I</span> <span begin="00:30.610" end="00:30.780">can</span><span begin="00:30.780" end="00:30.810">'t</span> <span begin="00:30.810" end="00:30.960">help</span> <span begin="00:31.010" end="00:31.080">but</span> <span begin="00:31.180" end="00:31.780">no</span><span begin="00:31.780" end="00:31.960">ti</span><span begin="00:32.000" end="00:32.060">ce</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不禁注意到</span></p>
      <p begin="00:32.340" end="00:35.780" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:32.340" end="00:32.510">You</span> <span begin="00:32.560" end="00:32.720">re</span><span begin="00:32.720" end="00:32.780">f</span><span begin="00:32.780" end="00:33.180">lec</span><span begin="00:33.330" end="00:33.520">ting</span> <span begin="00:33.520" end="00:33.640">thi</span><span begin="00:33.640" end="00:33.730">s</span> <span begin="00:33.730" end="00:33.910">hear</span><span begin="00:33.910" end="00:33.950">t</span> <span begin="00:33.950" end="00:33.990">of</span> <span begin="00:34.140" end="00:35.780">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你映照出了我的心</span></p>
      <p begin="00:37.020" end="00:42.640" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:37.020" end="00:37.170">I</span><span begin="00:37.170" end="00:37.230">f</span> <span begin="00:37.230" end="00:37.380">you</span> <span begin="00:37.430" end="00:37.930">e</span><span begin="00:37.990" end="00:38.530">ver</span> <span begin="00:38.580" end="00:38.800">feel</span> <span begin="00:38.800" end="00:38.990">a</span><span begin="00:38.990" end="00:39.510">lone</span> <span begin="00:39.590" end="00:39.930">and</span> <span begin="00:40.360" end="00:40.420">the</span> <span begin="00:40.530" end="00:40.580">g</span><span begin="00:40.580" end="00:41.040">lare</span> <span begin="00:41.100" end="00:41.200">ma</span><span begin="00:41.220" end="00:41.290">kes</span> <span begin="00:41.320" end="00:41.460">me</span> <span begin="00:41.510" end="00:41.670">hard</span> <span begin="00:41.720" end="00:41.790">to</span> <span begin="00:41.910" end="00:42.640">find</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">若你感到孤独 刺眼的光芒让你难以寻觅我</span></p>
      <p begin="00:42.860" end="00:48.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:42.860" end="00:42.940">Ju</span><span begin="00:42.940" end="00:43.010">st</span> <span begin="00:43.050" end="00:43.230">know</span> <span begin="00:43.250" end="00:43.440">that</span> <span begin="00:43.460" end="00:43.630">I'm</span> <span begin="00:43.650" end="00:44.210">al</span><span begin="00:44.240" end="00:44.540">way</span><span begin="00:44.540" end="00:44.570">s</span> <span begin="00:44.820" end="00:44.990">pa</span><span begin="00:45.020" end="00:45.180">ral</span><span begin="00:45.210" end="00:45.650">lel</span> <span begin="00:45.800" end="00:45.970">on</span> <span begin="00:45.990" end="00:46.160">the</span> <span begin="00:46.180" end="00:46.330">o</span><span begin="00:46.360" end="00:46.440">ther</span> <span begin="00:46.530" end="00:48.340">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请知晓我始终平行存在于另一侧</span></p>
      <p begin="00:48.680" end="00:51.840" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:48.680" end="00:48.830">'Cau</span><span begin="00:48.830" end="00:48.900">se</span> <span begin="00:48.900" end="00:49.040">with</span> <span begin="00:49.090" end="00:49.290">your</span> <span begin="00:49.340" end="00:49.510">hand</span> <span begin="00:49.510" end="00:49.650">in</span> <span begin="00:49.700" end="00:49.860">my</span> <span begin="00:49.910" end="00:50.420">hand</span> <span begin="00:50.470" end="00:50.640">and</span> <span begin="00:50.660" end="00:50.740">a</span> <span begin="00:50.850" end="00:50.990">po</span><span begin="00:51.050" end="00:51.130">cket</span> <span begin="00:51.230" end="00:51.430">ful</span><span begin="00:51.430" end="00:51.460">l</span> <span begin="00:51.460" end="00:51.500">of</span> <span begin="00:51.590" end="00:51.840">soul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为当你我携手 怀揣着满腔深情</span></p>
      <p begin="00:52.020" end="00:54.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:52.020" end="00:52.170">I</span> <span begin="00:52.240" end="00:52.340">can</span> <span begin="00:52.400" end="00:52.650">tell</span> <span begin="00:52.650" end="00:52.770">you</span> <span begin="00:52.790" end="00:52.890">there</span><span begin="00:52.890" end="00:52.970">'s</span> <span begin="00:53.030" end="00:53.430">no</span> <span begin="00:53.570" end="00:53.850">pla</span><span begin="00:53.850" end="00:53.920">ce</span> <span begin="00:53.940" end="00:54.100">we</span> <span begin="00:54.160" end="00:54.370">coul</span><span begin="00:54.370" end="00:54.510">dn't</span> <span begin="00:54.580" end="00:54.730">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我敢说没有我们无法抵达的远方</span></p>
      <p begin="00:54.930" end="00:58.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:54.930" end="00:55.030">Ju</span><span begin="00:55.030" end="00:55.090">st</span> <span begin="00:55.130" end="00:55.280">pu</span><span begin="00:55.280" end="00:55.320">t</span> <span begin="00:55.320" end="00:55.500">your</span> <span begin="00:55.500" end="00:55.730">han</span><span begin="00:55.730" end="00:55.750">d</span> <span begin="00:55.750" end="00:55.940">on</span> <span begin="00:55.940" end="00:56.020">the</span> <span begin="00:56.120" end="00:56.620">gla</span><span begin="00:56.620" end="00:56.690">ss,</span> <span begin="00:56.710" end="00:56.870">I'll</span> <span begin="00:56.910" end="00:57.020">be</span> <span begin="00:57.060" end="00:57.310">trying</span> <span begin="00:57.310" end="00:57.380">to</span> <span begin="00:57.470" end="00:57.630">pull</span> <span begin="00:57.630" end="00:57.790">you</span> <span begin="00:57.890" end="00:58.060">through</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将手贴在玻璃上 我会努力将你拉入怀中</span></p>
      <p begin="00:58.270" end="01:00.580" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:58.270" end="00:58.430">You</span> <span begin="00:58.460" end="00:58.560">ju</span><span begin="00:58.560" end="00:58.630">st</span> <span begin="00:58.650" end="00:58.840">got</span><span begin="00:58.850" end="00:58.970">ta</span> <span begin="00:59.040" end="00:59.110">be</span> <span begin="00:59.130" end="00:59.250">s</span><span begin="00:59.250" end="01:00.580">trong</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你只需坚强</span></p>
      <p begin="01:00.730" end="01:03.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:00.730" end="01:00.840">'Cau</span><span begin="01:00.840" end="01:00.890">se</span> <span begin="01:00.990" end="01:01.180">I</span> <span begin="01:01.190" end="01:01.350">don't</span> <span begin="01:01.390" end="01:01.540">want</span> <span begin="01:01.560" end="01:01.750">to</span> <span begin="01:01.780" end="01:02.120">lo</span><span begin="01:02.120" end="01:02.180">se</span> <span begin="01:02.180" end="01:02.250">you</span> <span begin="01:02.360" end="01:03.060">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我现在不想失去你</span></p>
      <p begin="01:03.510" end="01:06.390" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:03.510" end="01:03.680">I'm</span> <span begin="01:03.720" end="01:03.830">loo</span><span begin="01:03.900" end="01:04.090">king</span> <span begin="01:04.120" end="01:04.460">right</span> <span begin="01:04.480" end="01:04.590">at</span> <span begin="01:04.690" end="01:04.920">the</span> <span begin="01:04.920" end="01:05.230">o</span><span begin="01:05.280" end="01:05.380">ther</span> <span begin="01:05.490" end="01:05.670">hal</span><span begin="01:05.670" end="01:05.720">f</span> <span begin="01:05.720" end="01:05.780">of</span> <span begin="01:05.890" end="01:06.390">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我正注视着我的另一半</span></p>
      <p begin="01:07.030" end="01:09.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:07.030" end="01:07.120">The</span> <span begin="01:07.220" end="01:07.360">va</span><span begin="01:07.410" end="01:07.510">can</span><span begin="01:07.580" end="01:07.780">cy</span> <span begin="01:07.820" end="01:07.900">that</span> <span begin="01:07.950" end="01:08.190">sa</span><span begin="01:08.210" end="01:08.240">t</span> <span begin="01:08.240" end="01:08.360">in</span> <span begin="01:08.390" end="01:08.530">my</span> <span begin="01:08.620" end="01:09.360">heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我心中曾有的空缺</span></p>
      <p begin="01:09.740" end="01:12.480" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:09.740" end="01:09.890">I</span><span begin="01:09.890" end="01:09.960">s</span> <span begin="01:09.960" end="01:10.020">a</span> <span begin="01:10.040" end="01:10.110">s</span><span begin="01:10.170" end="01:10.830">pa</span><span begin="01:10.830" end="01:10.920">ce</span> <span begin="01:10.920" end="01:11.020">that</span> <span begin="01:11.120" end="01:11.260">now</span> <span begin="01:11.290" end="01:11.390">you</span> <span begin="01:11.510" end="01:12.480">hold</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如今已被你填满</span></p>
      <p begin="01:13.390" end="01:15.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:13.390" end="01:13.640">Show</span> <span begin="01:13.660" end="01:13.850">me</span> <span begin="01:13.870" end="01:14.010">how</span> <span begin="01:14.030" end="01:14.100">to</span> <span begin="01:14.220" end="01:14.430">fight</span> <span begin="01:14.610" end="01:14.700">for</span> <span begin="01:14.830" end="01:15.520">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">告诉我此刻该如何去争取</span></p>
